# Project data — regeneratable from data.refresh, but the canonical
# parquet is committed so the deployed dashboard has data without a
# cold-start API fetch.
*.parquet
!smard_merged_15min.parquet
*.csv
!smard_merged_15min_head.csv
# Dashboard / notebooks read these at runtime — keep tracked so the deployed
# app and notebooks render correctly.
